subnet_vox is a peer to peer chat application that uses UDP multicasts (broadcasts) for sending messages between clients in the subnet.

more info in this vid:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6VTIikP-eqE

to run (windows / linux):
1 - download latest release for your os
2 - in build folder find the client.exe / binary and run it

to build (windows / linux):
1 - clone / download
2 - open a terminal in ./subnet_vox directory
3 - in build commands.txt find the sequence that fits your os, execute all
4 - ./subnet_vox/build folder should appear with the client in it